      "text": "As expected, I found the Astrolabe in the Ritual Chamber, with the fifth parchment lying on its console—according to Empousa, this should be the last one. The content of this parchment is simple; it just asks me to meet her at the Observatory at midnight tonight.\n\nCome to think of it, thanks to Empousa, I've enjoyed a long-overdue \"tour\" of Bathory Castle, which wasn't half bad. I wonder what feelings Empousa held as she walked through this castle that now belongs entirely to her? I suppose I'll know the answer soon enough.",
